				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Once the chosen are all dead, and the netherbrain is free, it sends its minions (mindflayers and potentially Steel Watchers) after the player.  the Emperor reacts with this AD after combats with Mindflayers or Steel Watchers. He urges the player to get to the netherbrain, and warns that things are spinning out of control."
